  .card.h-100
    .card-body
      h4.card-title
        span.h2[style="#{initial_color}"]
          = initial
        = card_title
      p.card-text.text-left
        | こちらから
        = card_detail
        | を確認できます。
        | 使い方は
        = link_to "こちら", help_path
        | 。
    .card-footer
      = link_to "Find Out More!", card_path, class:  "btn btn-outline-secondary"
